{
  "title": "Site Induction Questionnaire - UK Construction Site",
  "elements": [
    {
      "element": "paragraph",
      "description": "Welcome and introduction",
      "html": "<h1>Welcome to Our Construction Site</h1><p>This induction questionnaire must be completed by all contractors, sub-contractors, and visitors before commencing work on site. Please complete all sections accurately and honestly. This information is required for health and safety compliance under UK Construction (Design and Management) Regulations 2015.</p><p><strong>Important:</strong> You must not commence work until this induction has been completed and approved by the Site Manager.</p>"
    },
