    {
      "element": "paragraph",
      "description": "Site Rules and Regulations",
      "html": "<h2>Site Rules and Regulations</h2><p>By signing this induction form, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to comply with the following site rules:</p><ul><li>Hard hats, high-visibility clothing, and safety footwear must be worn at all times on site</li><li>No smoking except in designated areas</li><li>No alcohol or illegal substances permitted on site</li><li>All accidents and near misses must be reported immediately</li><li>Only authorised personnel may operate plant and machinery</li><li>All visitors must sign in and out</li><li>Site speed limit: 5mph</li><li>Mobile phones should not be used while operating machinery or in safety-critical areas</li><li>All tools and equipment must be in good working order</li><li>Personal Protective Equipment (PPE) must be worn as required</li></ul>"
    },
